---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Lemony Roast Veggie Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt & Mint
description: Consider plain chicken breast strips a thing of the past: in this recipe, your chicken gets gussied up in a gorgeous golden
breadcrumb topping with complementary spices. You’ll pan-fry it for a healthier alternative, then lay it on a bed of lemony veggie
couscous and drizzle over garlicky yoghurt. Simple, satisfying, and supercharged with flavor—what more could you ask for?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crumbed-chicken-lemony-roast-veggie-couscous-889c6a5d.jpg
